# Coverage exclusions for acp-kit. File-level patterns only; no line
# numbers, no per-function regexes. See sibling .covignore in poe-acp /
# slack-acp for rationale.

# Per-package "must" helpers — files named *_must.go contain panic-only
# helpers for branches the production caller cannot trigger (kernel-level
# pipe allocation, post-success Close, etc.). Each helper carries a doc
# comment justifying why it is unreachable.
_must\.go:
